results.title: Watch and eye dock - iPhone 6 Plus
results.description:
The Watch and Eye dock is minimalistic and a feature rich solution to both charge and display your Iphone 6 or 6 Plus. This Dock/valet has an integrated slot that can keep 3 to 4 watches at the ready. A carved pocket in the base can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, or other items you may carry in your daily life. A slot to the side can securely store a wallet or check book. Additional storage can be found in the rear of the dock for keys or change etc. This dock was designed for an Iphone 6 with a case up to an otterbox in size or an iphone 6 Plus


The details: 

Easy access to all buttons and phone removal 

Curved wire path allows the phone and wire to be removed without disrupting the dock/valet. 

Slot provided for 3 to 4 watches, depending on size

Front pocket can store eyeglasses, sunglasses, pens etc.

Rear storage pockets can store keys, pocket change, ear-buds, and plenty of other items you may choose to carry in your pockets. 

Item ships USPS priority 1 to 3 day mail

This is meant to be used with an iphone 6 or 6-Plus

This docking station has been sanded smooth and finished with boiled linseed oil.

Aprx. 7 inches tall x 10 inches wide with a food print of 4 x 10 inches.  

Made out of Oak plywood in the USA by Chris Fandz

PLEASE NOTE: On hand stock quantities will vary. If this is for a gift and should ship out before 2 weeks after purchase, please send me a convo.
